---
title: Mango-Chilli Indian Pork & Carrot Couscous with Cucumber Raita
description: You can’t miss the signs that summer is here, so let’s heed the call to golden sunny days and cook up a bright serving of sunset carrot couscous and Mumbai spiced pork. That “Summer” element you can taste is the mango chilli sauce glazed over the pork. Enjoy!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
